OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1778087158
OL,3,C1 in 9 deliberately burn themselves in
OL,4,Chot weather, new stats reveal
OL,6,FA woman with stage 3 skin cancer is
OL,7,Fwarning people about the dangers of
OL,8,Fsun exposure, as new statistics reveal
OL,9,Fmore than 1 in 9 adults in Wales burn
OL,10,Ftheir skin on purpose from the sun or
OL,11,Fusing sun beds.
OL,13,FKate Howson from Cardiff was diagnosed
OL,14,Fwith Melanoma after returning home
OL,15,Ffrom travelling across the world in
OL,16,F2025. She first noticed a mole on her
OL,17,Flower back, which later changed in
OL,18,Fcolour a couple of months later.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
