FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1778087158
OL,3,C1 in 9 deliberately burn themselves in
OL,4,Chot weather, new stats reveal
OL,6,F"I just noticed an itch on my back, my
OL,7,Flower back, and it turned out to be a
OL,8,Fmole that I hadn't really noticed, but
OL,9,FI noticed it was a little bit red.
OL,10,FBut, we weren't going to be back home
OL,11,Ffor another couple of months so kind
OL,12,Fof just left it then" she said.
OL,14,FAfter contacting her GP, she was
OL,15,Freferred to a specialist
OL,16,Fdermatologist. They confirmed it was
OL,17,Fstage 2 skin cancer, which later
OL,18,Fprogressed to stage 3 after spreading
OL,19,Fto her groin.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1778087158
OL,3,C1 in 9 deliberately burn themselves in
OL,4,Chot weather, new stats reveal
OL,6,F"You don't expect it to happen, you
OL,7,Fdon't expect to be dealing with cancer
OL,8,Fwhen you're in your 30's, I think it
OL,9,Fdefinitely came as a shock."
OL,11,FNew research by the charity Melanoma
OL,12,FFocus found nearly one third of Welsh
OL,13,Fadults never use sunscreen during the
OL,14,Fsummer months.
OL,16,FIt also found that more than 1 in 9
OL,17,FWelsh adults have deliberately burnt
OL,18,Ftheir skin from the sun or using sun
OL,19,Fbeds and 22% have never heard of the
OL,20,FUV index.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1778087158
OL,3,C1 in 9 deliberately burn themselves in
OL,4,Chot weather, new stats reveal
OL,6,FReacting to the statistics, Kate
OL,7,Fdescribed the findings as "shocking."
OL,9,FShe said, "we do have a culture in the
OL,10,FUK that we want to make the most of
OL,11,Fthe sun while it's out, we want to get
OL,12,Fin the beer gardens, we want to enjoy
OL,13,Fthe sun with our friends, and I think
OL,14,Fyou can still do that but I think it's
OL,15,Fdoing it safely."
OL,17,FOncology Consultant, Dr Ricky Frazer,
OL,18,Fexplained there was obvious mental
OL,19,Fwellbeing benefits to being out in the
OL,20,Fsun, but more awareness of it's impact
OL,21,Fis needed.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1778087158
OL,3,C1 in 9 deliberately burn themselves in
OL,4,Chot weather, new stats reveal
OL,6,F"Getting burnt more than five times
OL,7,Fdoubles your chances of getting skin
OL,8,Fcancer in your life, so it's really
OL,9,Fimportant that people aren't setting
OL,10,Fout to burn themselves.
OL,12,F"It's important to cover up, it's
OL,13,Fimportant to avoid those hours where
OL,14,Fthe sun is most risky to the skin.
OL,16,F"Make it a habit to check the UV index
OL,17,Fdaily and wear sunscreen or cover your
OL,18,Fskin whenever it's 3 or above."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/6
